{
  "stem": "10359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then it was very hard financially because we only had what we could either sell, you know, [INAUDIBLE], so to say, or exchange different cosmetics or medication products for eggs or butter or bread.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I didn't feel it as much as others because we had the surplus of a lot of things left over from the drugstore that we can exchange for food products.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But other people had much, much worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then in thirty-- in-- from '39 to '41.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then in '41, the war broke out with Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that's how the whole Holocaust started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a lot of non-Jewish friends from the public school, high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I personally did not feel any.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some did, maybe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- I personally did not feel it, any anti-semitism because I was in the public school, and I had a lot of non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was quite comfortable in the whole environment, so to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the problem started in thirty-- the anti-semitism?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or in general with the problem with--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the Germans came in, naturally, it started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And thousands of Jews from Ostrog fled to Russia with the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to go, but I was a little bit late.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the time I arrived in a town about 30, 40 miles from Ostrog, the parachutes landed, and I had to go back to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first one-- when I came back from wherever I, I traveled, the first action started, I think, was August 4, 1941.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took all the people out from the homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They chased them out, so to say-- the police and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to have a special what they call [GERMAN] Kommando, which is a subgroup of the SS.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took them to a big place near the woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that time, they concentrated on old people, religious people, anybody who had a beard, or anybody who looked-- the sick people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They killed them-- it was about 3,000 of them-- in the ravines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They simply shot them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A month later-- now, we went back and we start-- people started to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I had to work with some people that I knew from my neighborhoods and rag business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had to collect rags and give them to, to the German army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they manufactured something from that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I also worked on trucks collecting furniture from the homes that they acquired-- the Germans-- Jewish homes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for a while, I did-- the first month, everything was very strange to me because I didn't know what will happen later on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought it's all a temporary type of a thing until everything will get organized in some way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after the second time, then I realized what's going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the second Aktion was about a month later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, they chased out the people from their homes, and they took them to a place near the-- near the woods.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this time they concentrated mostly on teenagers, people from schools, young people, most of my Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they say that they-- this time, they didn't shoot him, but they gassed them in trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, at that time I was at that-- at that place too together with all the other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they ask-- the Germans ask if, if you are carpenter, or electrician, or you have any kind of a trade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, I'm a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they probably needed carpenters or electricians, so they let me go with a few other people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I knew that they'll need some kind of tradespeople.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they'll-- so I told them I'm a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A friend of mine says he's electrician.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how they let us go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After that, I realized that this will be probably the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I felt like I'm in a time warp, so to say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know where I am.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody was walking, going to school, walking the streets, living a normal life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we are completely isolated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's like unbelievable feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are-- every day we are adrenaline high, so to say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are pushing [? nut ?] from minute to minute trying to survive and doing something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened after the second part.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you were home?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you didn't leave?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- we still-- I had-- I still had my home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this was only a month later, so they didn't liquidate anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
